cat("Greetings intelligent life form! You are currently receiving a message from a planet inhabited with other intelligent life, known as planet Earth. If you are receiving this message, that means you must be able to send one back, so I encourage you to transmit a reply. We here have no intention of bringing you harm. The people on Earth are interested in where you reside, how you live your life, and how far away you are (and also if you are actually out in space). We have been trying for years to reach out to you and have received no responses. Is there a reason we have not yet been in contact? We have many questions for you, so it is assumed that you would have questions about us as well It would benefit us both if you managed to contact us in some way. We hope to hear from you as well and that you can answer some of our questions.")